Standard: 好了，我会尽快把这批货物送到你的店铺上。
EN: Alright, I'll get this batch of goods delivered to your store as soon as possible.

Standard: 记住，经营是个长期过程，记得定期回来看看有什么新货。
EN: Remember, running a business is a long-term endeavor. Make sure to come back regularly to see what new items we have in stock.

Standard: 祝你生意兴隆，如果需要什么帮助，王叔这里随时欢迎你。
EN: Wishing you prosperity in your business, and remember, Mr.Wang is always here to help if you need anything.
